snippet.title: Chrysalis Trailer - Master UPC
snippet.description:
Official trailer for our game Chrysalis.
Project developed by students of the @upcschool Advanced Programming & Animation & Digital Arts for AAA Video Games. 

Further information in our website; rollingbarrel.github.io/
Chek out our Linkedin; linkedin.com/company/rolling-barrel/

Music done by Jose Sanchez Moya (@cheezie_j). 
You can see more of his work here (open.spotify.com/artist/0KOhoJcYsvYerz1BDbgNDr?si=9CKJgkPCTvmn3U5ClqSwfA)
